title: Team Leaden Looking for Members - TOP / MID / JG - Diamond 5 +
body:
Team Leaden is looking for players to fill its roster, we play in small tournaments primarily on weekends.
We are ideally looking for people with a strong will to improve and are able to effectively communicate within our team.

You will need to be free to play tournament games, (They generally start around 10am AEST and last a few hours after that)  and be able to play practice games during the week.
If you have any questions feel free to let me know, just add me in game : Zealitee
